     1                          ; Anatomy of a stack frame:
     2                          ; 
     3                          ; Number of pushed bytes (2*n)
     4                          ; Pushed word n-1
     5                          ; ...
     6                          ; Pushed word 0
     7                          ; ZZZZZZZZ ZZZZZZZZ
     8                          ; SPPPLLLL 0000EZZZ
     9                          ; Local variable k-1
    10                          ; ...
    11                          ; Local variable 0
    12                          ; 
    13                          ; S = Does return address point to a a variable where return value should be stored?
